data.description: Check out this well maintained, recently updated ranch, minutes from an elementary school, restaurants, shopping, interstate and Scott Air Force Base. The recent upgrades are new kitchen cabinetry, countertops, stove, all new flooring throughout the home. With new carpeting in the bedrooms just installed last week. This ranch has 3 bedrooms and 2 full updated baths, large living room and family room. The old laundry room has been turned into a mudroom/butlers pantry with the laundry hookups moved to the garage. Loads of entertaining can be done in the large fenced-in backyard. Call today for your favorite agent for a personal tour.  This is a coming soon, beginning Tuesday, April 23 with the property going live for showings on Friday, April 26th.
